---
title: Korean Style Gochujang Veggie Noodles with Tenderstem® Broccoli and Peanuts
description: Our Korean Style Gochujang Veggie Noodles is a delicious veggie option that makes it easy to eat more veg in your diet and try something new!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/HF_Y23_R41_W26_UK_R14546-7_Main_high-19ab4c65.jpg
